OL,3,CRiot accused 'encouraged youths'
OL,4,Cduring cafe attack
OL,6,FA Belfast man allegedly encouraged
OL,7,Fyouths as they destroyed a migrant-
OL,8,Fowned cafe during racial rioting on
OL,9,Fthe city's streets, a court has heard.
OL,11,FPolice also claimed Paul McCallister,
OL,12,F26, threw a bottle at a passing bus
OL,13,Fwhen violence flared following an anti-
OL,14,Fimmigration protest.
OL,16,FDetails emerged as McCallister, of
OL,17,FCity Way, was refused bail on charges
OL,18,Fof riotous assembly and intentionally
OL,19,Fencouraging or assisting rioters.
