OL,3,CRiot accused 'encouraged youths'
OL,4,Cduring cafe attack
OL,6,FThe father of one was arrested as part
OL,7,Fof investigations into the unrest
OL,8,Fwhich erupted on August 3 after the
OL,9,Fcity centre rally.
OL,11,FBelfast Magistrates' Court was told a
OL,12,Fcrowd initially headed towards the
OL,13,FIslamic Centre on University Street
OL,14,Fbefore sustained public disorder broke
OL,15,Fout in nearby areas.
OL,17,FPSNI officers came under attack as
OL,18,Fbusinesses and vehicles were set on
OL,19,Ffire on Donegall Road and Sandy Row.
