OL,3,CRiot accused 'encouraged youths'
OL,4,Cduring cafe attack
OL,6,FA detective said McCallister was
OL,7,Fidentified on CCTV recordings of those
OL,8,Fpresent at the scene of the trouble.
OL,10,F"Footage has captured the defendant
OL,11,Fappearing to encourage younger males
OL,12,Fwho were responsible for the
OL,13,Fdestruction of the Bash Cafe on
OL,14,FDonegall Road," he claimed.
OL,16,F"The defendant was also visible on
OL,17,FCCTV footage throwing what appears to
OL,18,Fbe a bottle in the direction of a
OL,19,Fpassing bus."
