OL,3,CRiot accused 'encouraged youths'
OL,4,Cduring cafe attack
OL,6,FDuring interviews McCallister admitted
OL,7,Fbeing in the footage standing with
OL,8,Fmasked youths involved in the public
OL,9,Fdisorder, the court heard.
OL,11,FHe claimed that he only threw a bottle
OL,12,Fof water at those who had damaged a
OL,13,Fcar belonging to a member of his
OL,14,Ffamily.
OL,16,FWhen police pointed out that the
OL,17,Fvehicle had left the area more than
OL,18,Ffive minutes earlier, he replied: "No
OL,19,Fcomment."
