OL,6,FMcCallister was also unable to account
OL,7,Ffor clothing he had worn on August 3.
OL,9,FOpposing bail, the detective stressed
OL,10,Fthat at least three businesses in the
OL,11,FBotanic and Sandy Row areas were burnt
OL,12,Fout that night.
OL,14,F"One of them had a set of apartments
OL,15,Fin which 42 people had to be evacuated
OL,16,Fby the Northern Ireland Fire Service,"
OL,17,Fhe added.
