OL,6,FEven though large-scale street
OL,7,Fdisorder has diminished since then,
OL,8,Fthe court heard police are still
OL,9,Fdealing with hate-related incidents of
OL,10,Fimmigrant families being targeted and
OL,11,Fproperties attacked.
OL,13,FDefence solicitor Una Conway argued
OL,14,FMcCallister knew nothing about the
OL,15,Fanti-immigration rally and denies
OL,16,Fthrowing a bottle at a bus.
