OL,3,CRiot accused 'encouraged youths'
OL,4,Cduring cafe attack
OL,6,F"He would say that what he did was
OL,7,Flittering, and he certainly wasn't
OL,8,Fencouraging others because he had
OL,9,Fabsolutely no idea what was going on,"
OL,10,Fshe submitted.
OL,12,FMs Conway described her client as a
OL,13,Fvulnerable man who suffers from
OL,14,Flearning difficulties and serious
OL,15,Fmental health problems.
OL,17,F"He is a vulnerable male, as a lot of
OL,18,Fthe males involved in the rioting are."
OL,20,FMcCallister was denied bail, however,
OL,21,Fbased on the risk of re-offending.
