OL,6,FRemanding him in custody until
OL,7,FSeptember 25, District Judge Anne
OL,8,FMarshall said: "Whilst these incidents
OL,9,Fmay have settled a little, they are
OL,10,Fextremely serious.
OL,12,F"They could start up again like that,
OL,13,Fif people like this defendant take to
OL,14,Fthe streets in protest."
